h they'd never known.) Things have been only a little different since then. They had a queue of videos ready to go already while you adjusted your schedule, but you've always uploaded in the middle of the night anyway, so there wasn't much change there, and they'd always been something of a recluse anyway. And outside of your trademark attire, you were sort of hard to recognize anyway. You had dipped their toes in critiquing other formats before, and, aside from video games, they felt that they could at least offer some of their trademark wit and tact to any artform that needed them. Now that they knew there is truth about vampires, and ghosts, and the like, they sought it out, so they could avoid overemphasizing that in their videos. Lately, youve been pressured to stop uploading altogether, and your worried that if they do that, not only would their income disappear, but they wouldn't be able to hold onto what made you a great critic in the first place."
        },
        {
          "staff_generated_concept": "Sire:",
          "column_2": "The Director",
          "column_3": "Reference: (If any)",
          "column_6": "Clan",
          "column_7": "Toreador - Entranced by Art"
        },
        {
          "staff_generated_concept": "Embrace Date:",
          "column_2": "2012-08-01 00:00:00",
          "column_3": "Embrace Location:",
          "column_4": "Chicago",
          "column_6": "Generation",
          "column_7": "Neonate 11"
        },
        {
          "staff_generated_concept": "Who You Know",
          "column_2": "Your relationship to these people is described. This may mean they do not know you."
        },
        {
          "staff_generated_concept": "Starting Goals",
          "column_2": "These are recomendations, not mandates."
        },
        {
          "staff_generated_concept": "Expand your Artistic credentials and critical analysis for other mediums. You're great with movies, but amateur at other things."
        },
        {
          "staff_generated_concept": "Prove to the other vampires that you're just as good as they are! You made your money being a critic, and you're proud of that! THERE IS ART IN THE CRITIQUE!"
        },
        {
          "staff_generated_concept": "Presence is Lovely, isn't it? Wouldn't it be even better if it worked through Video? You have no idea whether or not there's a way to make it work, but you're willing to find out!"
        },
